{"tid":1954960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海外抵港人士明起可選擇GOGOVAN或Pickupp上門收取檢測樣本","createTime":"2020-04-02T07:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T11:58:05.000Z","uid":95094,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9e7be7130dac1619d5649416ee4ba448d71aaa","tid":1954960,"uid":95094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"衞生署公布，從海外抵港人士由明日起，可選擇請GOGOVAN或Pickupp兩間公司，上門收取深喉唾液樣本瓶，再送到衞生署診所或公共衞生化驗服務處，服務費為100元，有關服務由市民自由選擇，直接與供應商聯絡和及付費。<br />\n<br />\n目前從海外抵港而沒有病徵的人士，可於抵港後立刻前往亞博臨時樣本採集中心，即場收集及交回深喉唾液樣本，或選擇在家居檢疫期間自行於居所收集樣本，然後透過親友交到收集診所。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署表示，為方便有關人士交回樣本，數碼港創業學會邀請旗下兩間初創企業，提供上門收取樣本速遞服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518423-20200402.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518423-20200402.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=e87bda98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518423-20200402.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c70a8b5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518423-20200402.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n藍店又贏"},{"pid":"9daa11e2f8767f2f2877d758c7fb8e2e758fc457","tid":1954960,"uid":95094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"藍色經濟圈"},{"pid":"b9ae996b2164e4b6a82e20ec718c08f494eeaf5b","tid":1954960,"uid":95094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"多謝政府幫助我地GOGOGO"},{"pid":"bd436f77444996b5cd64082f74878db0fb7be479","tid":1954960,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"504446f8b0b651e2800da7c1e57016d9398fc94a","tid":1954960,"ui